metadata.author: Yoto
metadata.description:
Music to help you focus and relax. Beautifully recorded piano pieces designed to aid mindful breath work and meditation.

Tracks include:
1) Dögun
2) Regn
3) Amma
4) Morgunsár
5) Fossar
6) Folald
7) Jökulá
8) Dagbjört
9) Dalvík
10) Logn
11) Tófan
12) Mold
13) Leysingar
14) Grámar
15) Afdrep
16) Melrakki
17) Fjara
18) Bogkrabbi
